==Introduction==
国産対空機銃兵装の強化バージョンです。<br>
25mm高角機銃の三連装型ですが、一度に撃てるわけではなく、一門ずつ順番に撃って銃身の加熱を防ぎます。<br>
従来の連装機銃や仮設の単装機銃を加え、この25mm三連装機銃が近接対空兵装の中核となりました。

''An enhanced version of the domestic anti-aircraft machine gun armament.''<br>
''Although it has a triple mounting of the 25mm high-angle machine gun, it does not shoot simultaneously, but one by one in order to prevent the barrels from overheating.''<br>
''In addition to the standard twin mounts and temporary single mounts, this 25mm triple machine gun formed the core of close-range anti-aircraft armament.''

